p: The yield of ZCO was about 2.1%. The chemical compositions of ZCO are shown in Table 1 and 37 constituents were identified. β-Ocimene was predominant component, accounting for 24.48% of the total. It was followed by (-)-α-pinene (16.56%), 4-carvomenthenol (11.61%), sabinene (10.81%), linalool (10.09%), o-cymene (3.56%), β-phellandrene (3.15%), limonene (2.63%), and α-terpineol (1.74%) (Table 1).
